## Database Schema (MySQL)

### `users` table
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | BIGINT PK AUTO_INCREMENT | |
| name | VARCHAR(100) | |
| email | VARCHAR(150) UNIQUE | |
| password | VARCHAR(255) | BCrypt hashed |
| role | ENUM('CITIZEN','ADMIN') | |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | |

### `issues` table
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | BIGINT PK AUTO_INCREMENT | |
| title | VARCHAR(200) | |
| description | TEXT | |
| category | ENUM('POTHOLE','STREETLIGHT','GARBAGE','WATER_LEAKAGE','OTHER') | |
| status | ENUM('OPEN','IN_PROGRESS','RESOLVED','REJECTED') | |
| image_url | VARCHAR(500) | stored path |
| location | VARCHAR(300) | address string |
| latitude | DECIMAL(9,6) | optional GPS |
| longitude | DECIMAL(9,6) | optional GPS |
| upvotes | INT DEFAULT 0 | |
| user_id | BIGINT FK в†’ users.id | reporter |
| assigned_to | BIGINT FK в†’ users.id | admin |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMP | |

### `comments` table
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | BIGINT PK AUTO_INCREMENT | |
| content | TEXT | |
| issue_id | BIGINT FK в†’ issues.id | |
| user_id | BIGINT FK в†’ users.id | |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | |

---

## Backend API Endpoints

### Auth (`/api/auth`)
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Access |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/register` | Register new citizen | Public |
| POST | `/login` | Login, returns JWT | Public |

### Issues (`/api/issues`)
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Access |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/` | List all issues (filterable) | Public |
| GET | `/{id}` | Get single issue | Public |
| POST | `/` | Submit new issue + image | Citizen |
| PUT | `/{id}/upvote` | Upvote an issue | Citizen |
| GET | `/my` | Get current user's issues | Citizen |
| DELETE | `/{id}` | Delete own issue | Citizen/Admin |

### Admin (`/api/admin`)
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Access |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/issues` | All issues with filters | Admin |
| PUT | `/issues/{id}/status` | Update issue status | Admin |
| PUT | `/issues/{id}/assign` | Assign to admin | Admin |
| POST | `/issues/{id}/comment` | Add resolution comment | Admin |
| GET | `/stats` | Dashboard statistics | Admin |
| GET | `/users` | List all users | Admin |

### Files (`/api/files`)
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Access |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/{filename}` | Serve uploaded image | Public |

---

## Frontend Pages & Routes

| Route | Component | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `/` | Home | Landing page + featured issues |
| `/login` | Login | Login form |
| `/register` | Register | Citizen registration |
| `/issues` | IssueList | Browse + filter all issues |
| `/issues/:id` | IssueDetail | Full issue view + comments |
| `/report` | ReportIssue | Submit a new issue (Citizen) |
| `/profile` | Profile | View/edit own profile + my issues |
| `/admin` | AdminDashboard | Admin stats overview |
| `/admin/issues` | AdminIssues | Manage all issues |
| `/admin/users` | AdminUsers | View all registered users |

---

## Core Feature Modules

### 1. Authentication & Authorization
- JWT-based stateless auth via `Spring Security`
- Roles: `CITIZEN` and `ADMIN`
- Passwords hashed with BCrypt
- `@PreAuthorize` annotations on admin endpoints
- Frontend `AuthContext` + `ProtectedRoute`

### 2. Issue Reporting
- Form: title, description, category, location (text + optional GPS), image upload
- Image stored on server filesystem; URL saved in DB
- Category filter: Pothole, Streetlight, Garbage, Water Leakage, Other

### 3. Issue Tracking (Citizen View)
- Status: `OPEN в†’ IN_PROGRESS в†’ RESOLVED / REJECTED`
- Upvoting to surface community-priority issues
- My Issues page for tracking own reports
- Real-time status display with colour-coded badges

### 4. Admin Dashboard
- Card stats: Total, Open, In Progress, Resolved
- Table of all issues with filter & sort
- Inline status update dropdown
- Assign issue to self / other admins
- Add resolution comments

### 5. File Upload
- Spring `MultipartFile` API
- Image saved to `uploads/` directory
- Served via static resource mapping
- Frontend drag-and-drop image picker

### 6. Comment/Activity Thread
- Citizens and admins can comment on issues
- Shown on IssueDetail page as a thread

