## Verification Plan

### Backend Verification
Run Spring Boot app and test via Swagger UI:
```
# Start backend
cd backend
./mvnw spring-boot:run

# Open Swagger UI
http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html
```

Test scenarios manually via Swagger:
1. `POST /api/auth/register` вЂ“ register a citizen
2. `POST /api/auth/login` вЂ“ get JWT token
3. `POST /api/issues` (with token) вЂ“ submit issue with image
4. `GET /api/issues` вЂ“ verify issue appears
5. `PUT /api/admin/issues/{id}/status` (admin token) вЂ“ change status
6. `GET /api/admin/stats` вЂ“ verify dashboard stats

### Frontend Verification
```
# Start frontend dev server
cd frontend
npm run dev
# Opens at http://localhost:5173
```

Manual test flows:
1. Register в†’ Login в†’ Report Issue в†’ check My Issues page
2. Login as Admin в†’ view Dashboard в†’ update issue status
3. Browse Issues page в†’ verify filters work
4. Upload image in report form в†’ verify it shows in detail view

### Database Verification
```sql
-- Check tables
SHOW TABLES;
SELECT * FROM users;
SELECT * FROM issues;
SELECT * FROM comments;
```

