## Development Phases

| Phase | Work |
|---|---|
| **Phase 1** | Spring Boot project init, DB setup, User entity + Auth (JWT) |
| **Phase 2** | Issue entity, CRUD APIs, File upload, Admin APIs |
| **Phase 3** | React project init, Auth pages (Login/Register), Context |
| **Phase 4** | Issue pages (List, Detail, Report), Admin Dashboard pages |
| **Phase 5** | Styling (CSS design system), responsive layout |
| **Phase 6** | Integration testing, bug fixing, cleanup |
